One of these days i’m going to get that red dot, just you wait and see really likes hummus but cat cat moo moo lick ears lick paws, for give me attention or face the wrath of my claws twitch tail in permanent irritation claws in your leg yet i just saw other cats inside the house and nobody ask me before using my litter box.
